Van der Valk Hotel 's-Hertogenbosch - Vught is located in Vught and easily accessible from the A2 and N65. There is free parking, and the center of 's-Hertogenbosch is a 5-minute car ride away. There is a bus stop across the road. All rooms have air conditioning, a balcony and a private bathroom with a separate bathtub and walk-in shower. There is a restaurant, a lounge and a piano bar. The terrace is nice during summer days and you can make use of the fitness room and sauna next door. The Efteling is located a 20-minute car ride from Van der Valk 's Hertogenbosch - Vught. There are various possibilities to walk and cycle in the surrounding area. The hotel also offers a taxi service that can bring guests to the city center of 's-Hertogenbosch.

Couples in particular like the location – they rated it 8.0 for a two-person trip.

Refundable damage deposit
A damage deposit of € 200 is required on arrival. This will be collected by credit card. You should be reimbursed on check-out. Your deposit will be refunded in full by credit card, subject to an inspection of the property.

Must-know information for guests at this property

Guests are required to show a photo ID and credit card upon check-in. Please note that all Special Requests are subject to availability and additional charges may apply.

Guests under the age of 18 can only check in with a parent or official guardian.

A damage deposit of € 200 is required on arrival. This will be collected by credit card. You should be reimbursed on check-out. Your deposit will be refunded in full by credit card, subject to an inspection of the property.
